#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.rand.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.rand"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rand.rand:1 of
msgid "Random values in a given shape."
msgstr "给定形状的随机值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rand.rand:3 of
msgid ""
"Create a tensor of the given shape and populate it with random samples "
"from a uniform distributionc over ``[0, 1)``."
msgstr "创建给定形状的张量，并用 ``[0, 1)`` 上均匀分布的随机样本填充它。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rand.rand of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rand.rand:7 maxframe.tensor.random.rand.rand:10
#: maxframe.tensor.random.rand.rand:13 maxframe.tensor.random.rand.rand:16 of
msgid ""
"The dimensions of the returned tensor, should all be positive. If no "
"argument is given a single Python float is returned."
msgstr "返回张量的维度，应均为正数。如果没有提供参数，则返回一个 Python 浮点数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rand.rand of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rand.rand:20 of
msgid "**out** -- Random values."
msgstr "**out** -- 随机值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rand.rand of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rand.rand:21 of
msgid "Tensor, shape ``(d0, d1, ..., dn)``"
msgstr "Tensor, 形状 ``(d0, d1, ..., dn)``"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rand.rand:23 of
msgid ":py:obj:`random`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rand.rand:26 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rand.rand:27 of
msgid ""
"This is a convenience function. If you want an interface that takes a "
"shape-tuple as the first argument, refer to mt.random.random_sample ."
msgstr ""
"这是一个便捷函数。如果你希望使用以形状元组作为第一个参数的接口，请参考 mt"
".random.random_sample 。"

